<Layout 
  title="Image Aspect Ratio Guide: Understanding Picture Ratios for Every Platform 2025"
  description="Complete guide to image aspect ratios. Learn what 3:2, 4:3, 16:9, and 1:1 mean, how to change aspect ratios, and the correct picture ratio for every platform."
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-[80px] md:mt-10">

    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
